song_name: I Will Never Be The Same

version_description: Based on Melissa's MTV Unplugged preformance 3-21-95 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zjxS9PIv1_g.
This was taken from watching her live performances. She seems to play it in this key every time.
No capo, standard tuning. no other tabs on site, so i tried to pick it out. It does sound accurate. Play around with variations of F#m and D for better sound.
This version of PULSE was transcribed from the recording that Melissa Etheridge made two days after the PULSE nightclub massacre.
Acoustic, simple version. The bass guitar takes up the walkdown. The intro is a bit of a lilt and the A is a brief 1 beat against the repetitions of the D.
